I'm sure you have recently heard that Facebook has made a stand against our first and second amendment rights and has been systematically removing any and all firearm related pages from their site. Sure, this may be their right as a corporation. However, you and I as American citizens and second amendment supporters also have a right to stand up for what we believe in and that's what we need to do. I ask you to do as I did over a year ago and say "enough is enough!" Enough restrictions and scare tactics with the guns. Enough invasion of privacy. I am not affiliated with this organization in any way, I would just love to see facebook's stock fall a few more percentage points :) thank you for your time. Together, we can save this great country.
